OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,7,Fwith outbreaks of light rain possible
OL,8,Fat times. Windy over the hills and
OL,9,Fcoasts, breezy elsewhere. Mild
OL,10,Fovernight temperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA largely cloudy day,
OL,13,Fespecially across western hills. A
OL,14,Fchance of some light rain late
OL,15,Fmorning. Sunny intervals developing in
OL,16,Fthe east later in the day. Winds
OL,17,Feasing. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
